            "Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist, long wavy brown hair, piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, holding a crumbling ancient parchment map in the dense Amazon rainforest. Sunlight filters through the thick canopy above. Determination on her face. Cinematic lighting with god rays. Speech bubble saying in Turkish: 'Dede'min haritası... Beni buraya kadar getirdi.' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, dramatic cinematic lighting, borderless, full frame, no white borders.",
