            "Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist, long wavy brown hair, piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, kneeling beside an ancient moss-covered stone totem shaped like a jaguar head. She is brushing dirt off the stone. Look of discovery and excitement. Dappled forest lighting. Speech bubble saying in Turkish: 'Bu Jaguar Tanrısı sembolü... Giriş yakın olmalı.' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, dramatic cinematic lighting, borderless, full frame, no white borders.",
            "Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist, long wavy brown hair, piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, diving mid-air to dodge a swinging log trap triggered from the trees. Dynamic action pose, debris flying, blurred background due to speed. Shocked and alert expression. High contrast dramatic lighting. Speech bubble saying in Turkish: 'Lanet olsun! Tuzaklar hala çalışıyor!' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, dramatic cinematic lighting, borderless, full frame, no white borders.",
            "Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist, long wavy brown hair, piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, standing her ground against a shadowy, large spiritual Jaguar guardian with glowing eyes blocking the path. Maya looks brave but cautious. Mystical blue and purple lighting mixing with jungle green. Speech bubble saying in Turkish: 'Geçmeme izin ver! Sadece gerçeği arıyorum.' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, dramatic cinematic lighting, borderless, full frame, no white borders.",
            "Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist, long wavy brown hair, piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, standing on a cliff edge, overlooking a magnificent golden ancient Mayan city hidden in a valley below. Wide angle shot, epic scale. Face illuminated by the golden reflection of the city. Speech bubble saying in Turkish: 'Sonunda... Kayıp Şehir Xibalba!' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, dramatic cinematic lighting, borderless, full frame, no white borders.",
            "Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist, long wavy brown hair, piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, holding a glowing jade artifact inside the central temple. The artifact emits a magical green light illuminating her face. A smile of triumph and relief. Atmospheric temple interior lighting. Speech bubble saying in Turkish: 'Bunu başardım dede. Mirasın güvende.' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, dramatic cinematic lighting, borderless, full frame, no white borders.",
            "Sahne 8: Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, looks up in sudden alarm as the ancient temple begins to tremble violently. Dust and small stone debris are falling from the high stone ceiling, blurring the air around her. She clutches the glowing jade artifact tightly to her chest with both hands. The atmospheric green light of the temple shifts to an ominous, unstable flickering shadow. The walls covered in hieroglyphs seem to be cracking. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Hayır! Tapınak çöküyor! Tuzak mekanizmasını tetikledim!' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, dramatic cinematic lighting, motion lines, borderless, full frame, no white borders.",
            "Sahne 9: Dynamic action shot of Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, sprinting through a narrow stone corridor. Her hair is whipping back as she runs towards the camera. Behind her, massive stone blocks are crashing down, creating a cloud of dust and destruction. She holds the glowing jade artifact in one hand while using the other to balance. The lighting is high contrast, with beams of light cutting through the rising dust. Sweat glistens on her forehead. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Çıkışa ulaşmalıyım! Acele et Maya!' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, dramatic cinematic lighting, intense action blur, borderless, full frame, no white borders.",
            "Sahne 10: Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, skids to a halt as spectral, shadowy Mayan jaguar warriors materialize from the walls, blocking her path. Their eyes glow with a menacing red energy. Maya stands in a defensive combat stance, holding the jade artifact forward like a shield, its green light clashing with the red eyes of the guardians. The environment is dark and claustrophobic. Detailed texture on the spectral forms and Maya's determined expression. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Koruyucular... Efsaneler gerçekmiş!' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, dramatic cinematic lighting, supernatural elements, borderless, full frame, no white borders.",
            "Sahne 11: A breathtaking wide angle shot of Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, leaping across a deep chasm that has opened up in the temple floor. The pit below is filled with sharp obsidian spikes. She is mid-air, arms outstretched, reaching for a vine hanging from the crumbling ceiling. The jade artifact is secured in a pouch at her hip, glowing faintly. The perspective is from above, looking down into the danger, emphasizing the height and risk. Debris falls into the pit alongside her. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Tutunmam lazım... Şimdi!' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, dramatic cinematic lighting, extreme perspective, borderless, full frame, no white borders.",
            "Sahne 12: Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, bursting out of the temple entrance into the blinding sunlight of the Amazon jungle. She lands on her knees in the tall grass, gasping for breath, looking back as the temple entrance seals itself with a loud thud of stone against stone. Her clothes are covered in dust and grime, but she is safe. The jungle is lush and vibrant green around her. She holds the jade artifact up, looking at it with a mix of exhaustion and victory. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Güvendeyim... Ama bu sadece başlangıçtı.' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, dramatic cinematic lighting, strong contrast between dark temple and bright nature, borderless, full frame, no white borders.",
            "Sahne 13: A close-up, intimate shot of Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants covered in temple dust, sitting on a mossy log in the dense Amazon jungle. She has pulled an old, weathered paper map from her pocket and is holding the glowing green jade artifact over a specific section of it. The sunlight filters through the canopy in dappled patterns, illuminating the map where the artifact touches it, revealing hidden UV ink lines connecting geographical points. Maya's expression is one of sudden realization and awe as she deciphers the clue. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Dede... Haklıydın. Bu taş sadece bir hazine değil, haritanın eksik parçası!' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, dramatic cinematic lighting, soft bokeh background, borderless, full frame, no white borders.",
            "Sahne 14: A tense, medium shot showing Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, suddenly freezing in place. In the blurred background behind her, three menacing, armed mercenaries in dark tactical gear emerge from the thick ferns, spotting her. The atmosphere shifts from discovery to immediate danger. Maya's head is turned slightly, her blue eyes wide with alert, clutching the map and artifact tight to her chest. The jungle around them is dense with vines and tropical flowers. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Takip ediliyorum... Gölge Şirketi beni nasıl buldu?' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, dramatic cinematic lighting, suspenseful atmosphere, borderless, full frame, no white borders.",
            "Sahne 15: An action-packed dynamic angle shot of Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, sprinting through the dense undergrowth. She is vaulting over a massive fallen tree trunk with athletic precision, her hair flowing wildly behind her. The mercenaries are visible in the distance, chasing her, hacking through the foliage with machetes. The perspective is low to the ground, emphasizing her speed and agility. Leaves and dirt fly up around her boots. The jade artifact is securely tucked in her belt pouch. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Onlara bunu kaptıramam! Nehir yolunu kullanmalıyım.' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, motion blur effects, dramatic cinematic lighting, borderless, full frame, no white borders.",
            "Sahne 16: A stealthy scene showing Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, hiding inside the hollow of a gigantic ancient Banyan tree. She is pressing her back against the wood, breathing heavily but silently. The lighting is dim and moody, with only narrow shafts of light piercing the darkness. In her hands, the jade artifact is pulsing with a rhythmic green light, acting like a compass, pointing deeper into the dark forest away from her pursuers. Her face is illuminated by the ghostly green glow of the stone. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Işık zayıflıyor... Ama yolu gösteriyor. Şelalenin arkasında olmalı.' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, high contrast chiaroscuro lighting, mystical atmosphere, borderless, full frame, no white borders.",
            "Sahne 17: A majestic wide-angle landscape shot featuring Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, standing at the edge of a high rocky cliff overlooking a massive waterfall. The sun is setting, casting a golden hour glow over the scene. Through the mist of the waterfall, the silhouette of a massive, golden Maya pyramid is barely visible, hidden from the naked eye but revealed by the angle of the light. Maya stands triumphant, wind blowing through her hair, looking out at the destination she finally found. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Kayıp Şehir... Bunca zaman gözümüzün önündeymiş.' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, epic scale, dramatic cinematic lighting, atmospheric perspective, borderless, full frame, no white borders.",
            "Sahne 18: High-angle action shot looking down a slippery rope as Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, rappels down the side of the cliff towards the base of the thundering waterfall. Her hair is whipping in the wind and her clothes are dampened by the mist. The setting sun casts deep orange and purple shadows across the wet rocks. The massive silhouette of the pyramid is looming closer through the water spray. She looks focused and determined. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Sadece biraz daha aşağıya... Giriş tam şelalenin kalbinde.' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, dynamic perspective, motion blur, borderless, full frame, no white borders.",
            "Sahne 19: Atmospheric medium shot showing Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, standing on a narrow, mossy ledge behind the curtain of the massive waterfall. The roar of the water is visually represented by vibration lines. It is dark and damp, but the jade artifact in her hand is glowing intensely bright green, illuminating a wall of ancient, vine-covered stone blocking her path. Her hair is wet and slicked back. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Taş çıldırmış gibi titriyor... Kapı burada olmalı.' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, high contrast, mystical lighting, wet texture rendering, borderless, full frame, no white borders.",
            "Sahne 20: Close-up detail shot focusing on Maya's hands and face. Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, places the glowing jade artifact into a perfectly shaped indentation in the center of a circular stone mechanism carved with terrified Mayan faces. The stone door is beginning to crack open, releasing stale, ancient air and dust. The green light from the artifact flows like liquid into the carvings of the door. Maya's expression is one of awe. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Dedemin haritasındaki sembol... Sonunda eşleşti.' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, magical glow effects, cinematic composition, borderless, full frame, no white borders.",
            "Sahne 21: Epic wide-angle shot revealing the interior of the Lost City's antechamber. Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, stands silhouetted against the opening door, stepping into a colossal hall. The hall is lit by lines of blue bioluminescent fungi growing on massive pillars. The floor is not solid but consists of floating stone platforms over a dark, bottomless abyss. The architecture is terrifyingly grand. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Bu mimari... İnsan yapımı gibi durmuyor.' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, atmospheric perspective, deep shadows, scale contrast, borderless, full frame, no white borders.",
            "Sahne 22: Tense over-the-shoulder shot looking past Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants. She has frozen in her tracks on the first stone platform. Deep in the shadows of the temple columns, pairs of glowing yellow eyes are appearing, accompanied by the silhouettes of Jaguar warriors wielding obsidian blades. The atmosphere shifts from wonder to immediate danger. Maya reaches for her belt, ready to run or fight. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Koruyucular... Efsaneler gerçekmiş.' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, chiaroscuro lighting, suspenseful atmosphere, borderless, full frame, no white borders.",
            "Sahne 23: Dynamic low-angle action shot capturing the immediate explosion of violence. Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, is captured mid-motion, diving to her right. A Jaguar warrior, muscular and adorned with feathers and jade, slashes down with a jagged obsidian sword exactly where she stood a second ago. Sparks fly where the blade hits the stone platform. The background is a blur of blue bioluminescence and dark stone. Maya's face shows fierce determination mixed with adrenaline. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Sayıları çok fazla! Savaşarak kazanamam!' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, motion lines, diagonal composition, dramatic lighting, borderless, full frame.",
            "Sahne 24: Wide shot emphasizing the perilous environment. Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, is sprinting across the floating stone platforms suspended over the endless black abyss. The platforms are disjointed, forcing her to leap dangerously. Behind her, three silhouettes of Jaguar warriors are pursuing with supernatural speed, their yellow eyes leaving trails in the dark. The cavern is immense, filled with glowing blue fungi that highlight the dust kicked up by the chase. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Köprü yıkılmış... Karşıya atlamam gerek!' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, atmospheric perspective, cinematic wide angle, borderless, full frame.",
            "Sahne 25: Intense close-up on Maya's hands and belt area as she runs. Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, fumbles to pull a red emergency flare from her tactical belt. The background is a rushing blur of ancient stone textures. In the periphery, a spear whizzes past her arm, tearing a small piece of her khaki sleeve. The lighting is a mix of the ambient cool blue and the warm anticipation of the flare. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Belki ateş onları yavaşlatır.' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, shallow depth of field, action focus, borderless, full frame.",
            "Sahne 26: A visually striking scene of contrast. Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, holds the ignited red flare high above her head. The harsh red light cuts through the blue bioluminescent atmosphere, creating dramatic purple shadows. The Jaguar warriors recoil, shielding their sensitive eyes, hissing in the darkness. Maya stands momentarily triumphant on a central platform, looking back at her pursuers. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Işıktan korkuyorlar! Bu bana zaman kazandırır.' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, chiaroscuro, heavy contrast, dramatic pose, borderless, full frame.",
            "Sahne 27: Point-of-view shot looking past Maya's shoulder towards a massive destination. Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, is panting heavily. Ahead of her, at the end of the floating platforms, stands a colossal circular stone door covered in rotating glyph rings. The door is sealed shut. The scale of the door dwarfs her, making the task seem impossible. The flare in her hand smokes, casting drifting shadows. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'İşte orada... İç Tapınağın kapısı.' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, grand scale, epic composition, borderless, full frame.",
            "Sahne 28: Close-up detail shot of the puzzle mechanism. Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, is frantically spinning a heavy stone ring on the door. Her face is beaded with sweat, illuminated by the dying red light of the flare she has stuck into a crack nearby. Her blue eyes scan the ancient Mayan glyphs rapidly. Behind her, out of focus, the warriors are recovering and approaching again. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Güneş, Jaguar, Yılan... Büyükbabanın notları... Neydi o sıralama?' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, texture focus, suspenseful atmosphere, borderless, full frame.",
            "Sahne 29: High-tension action shot. A Jaguar warrior has leaped onto the final platform, just inches behind Maya. Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, screams as she uses her whole body weight to turn the final stone mechanism. The warrior raises his obsidian macuahuitl (club) for a killing blow. The stone door begins to grind and rumble, emitting a golden light from the seams. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Hadi! Açıl artık!' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, dynamic posing, imminent danger, heavy shadows, borderless, full frame.",
            "Sahne 30: A spectacular scene of release and escape. The circular door rolls open, releasing a blinding golden light that blasts outward. Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, dives through the opening gap near the floor. The blast of light knocks the Jaguar warrior backward into the abyss. The contrast between the dark blue/red outside and the pure gold inside is stark. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Şimdi!' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, volumetric lighting, motion blur, dramatic impact, borderless, full frame.",
            "Sahne 31: Interior shot, low angle. Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, is lying on a smooth, golden floor, coughing and catching her breath. Behind her, the massive stone door slams shut with a heavy thud, sealing the darkness out. She is bathed in a warm, ethereal glow coming from the room's ceiling. Her clothes are dusty and slightly torn, but she is safe. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Son saniyede... Kapandı.' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, warm color palette, relief atmosphere, borderless, full frame.",
            "Sahne 32: Wide establishing shot of the new location. Maya, a stunningly beautiful female archaeologist with long wavy brown hair and piercing blue eyes, wearing a fitted khaki explorer shirt and cargo pants, slowly stands up, looking around in awe. She is in the 'Hall of Stars,' a vast chamber where the ceiling is embedded with glittering crystals mimicking the night sky. In the center sits a pristine emerald altar. The atmosphere is peaceful, silent, and ancient, a sharp contrast to the chaos outside. Speech bubble in Turkish: 'Burası... Haritada bile yoktu. Yıldızlar Salonu.' Style features: Comic book style, masterpiece, vibrant colors, highly detailed, magical atmosphere, grand architecture, wondrous tone, borderless, full frame."
